  "texts": [
    "The result of combining model outputs is a single prediction.",
    "A weighted vote facilitates classification, whereas a weighted average reduces numerical prediction.",
    "This approach is used by bagging and boosting; however, their respective models are generated uniquely [131].",
    "Stacking enables the combination of fundamental learning algorithms.",
    "Diversified foundation models allow the stacked ensemble to learn from various perspectives, producing heterogeneous features."
  ]
}